column5: Is there any place to buy leeches in Ear Falls? If not, where is the best place in Dryden?
There is a real nice store in Ear Falls. Prices are pretty reasonable. You come to it just as you cross the English R. on the right side. We buy our leeches there on our way up to Red Lake.
4 seasons sports 807-222 2200 . Be sure to call ahead to place your order, leeches are in short supply up there.
Hey, thanks, Big Tim. I called up there and Michael was a big help.
